  <brief_title>Real-World Betaseron Health Economic Outcomes Study for Relapsing Forms of Multiple Sclerosis</brief_title>
  <acronym>ROBUST</acronym>
  <official_title>Real-World Betaseron® Outcomes Study (ROBUST): A Twelve-month, US Prospective, Observational, Open-label, Single-arm, Multi-center Outcomes Study of Interferon β-1b (Betaseron®) Given Every Other Day for Relapsing Forms of Multiple Sclerosis</official_title>
