  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A Web based real world observational study in Relapsing-Remitting Multiple Sclerosis (RRMS)
      population capturing outcomes reported by patients and by the physicians during 12 months
      after initiating or resuming Betaseron.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
